reviewText: This Gadget Boy series is about saving the history from spydra; but he help famous people like charlie chapin, King Henry the 1st and others famous people but the story still the same.
My kids love this show. It sounds a lot like Inspector Gadget. We play it in the car so I haven't actually seen it yet.
Brought it for future use. I like buying as complete series for kids in affordable price and hope they can really learn it.
Great item at a great price. My son loved it. Item arrived on time and as described. Would highly recommend to others.

Ended up garage sale-ing this.  I liked the idea, but the cartoon was just too quirky, and stunted.  We watched 3 full episodes,but it just didn't get better and my kids wanted it to end.  Someone should redo this material in a better manner...as the content is very cool.

We love Gadget Boy, but this DVD's packaging is not the best. It comes in 3 different sleeves tucked inside the exterior DVD case. That's the only reason this DVD isn't 5 stars for us.
